quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  25,73,"And those who, when they are reminded of the Ayât (proofs, evidence, verses, lessons, signs, revelations, etc.) of their Lord, fall not deaf and blind thereat."
  25,74,"And those who say: "
  25,75,"Those will be rewarded with the highest place (in Paradise) because of their patience. Therein they shall be met with greetings and the word of peace and respect."
  26,46,"And the sorcerers fell down prostrate."
  26,47,"Saying: "
  26,48,""
  27,19,"So he [Sulaimân (Solomon)] smiled, amused at her speech{1} and said: ",footnotes:1:[{27:19} See the footnote of (Verse 6:143).]
  27,20,"He inspected the birds, and said: "
  27,21,""